<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.2">
<l>eṉvil valikaṇṭu pōveṉ ṟetirvantāṉ</l>
<l>taṉvil liṉōṭun tavattai yetirvāṅki</l>
<l>muṉvil valittu mutupeṇ ṇuyiruṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>taṉvilliṉ vaṉmaiyaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">tācarati taṉmaiyaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about the strength of the bow of him who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having taken and bent the virtue along with the bow of him</l>
<l rend="indent">who came as a rival saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Go look at the strength of my bow”</l>
<l>before seizing the bow,</l>
<l rend="indent">consumed the life of the old woman.</l>
<l>Jump and sing about the nature of Dāśarathi!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
